com.google.gwt.gwtai.applet.client
Interface AppletCallback<T>

Type Parameters:
T - The type of value this AppletCallback handles.
public interface AppletCallback<T>

The interface one must implement to receive responses from an applet. By registering a AppletCallback object with an applet, data can be sent back to the GWT application from within the applet code.

Adrian Buerki
